### PetClinic Pets API - Sample Requests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7120

@ownerId = "786ff4d9-8042-4518-9828-b8319d92e13c"
@petId = "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"  

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create Pet
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fluffy",
  "petType": "Cat",
  "breed": "Persian",
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}"
}

### Create Another Pet
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buddy",
  "petType": "Dog",
  "breed": "Golden Retriever",
  "birthDate": "2019-07-20T00:00:00Z",
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}"
}

### Create Pet without Birth Date
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Whiskers",
  "petType": "Cat",
  "breed": "Siamese",
  "birthDate": null,
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}"
}

### Get Pet by ID (replace {petId} with actual pet ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/{petId}

### Get Pets by Owner ID (replace {ownerId} with actual owner ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets?ownerId={{ownerId}}

### Update Pet (replace {petId} with actual pet ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pets/{petId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fluffy",
  "petType": "Cat",
  "breed": "Persian",
  "birthDate": "2020-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "ownerId": "{ownerId}"
}
